      • getWeightedMiddle

        public static java.util.Date getWeightedMiddle(java.util.List<VaultEntry> data,
                                               VaultEntryType type)
        Calculates the timepoint of the weighted middle of a specific Type in a given VaultEntry list, using the value of a VaultEntry as weight.

        More precisely, it calculates:
        (date1*value1 + date2*value2 +...) / (value1 + value2 + ...)

        Parameters:
        data - List in which the weighted middle is searched for
        type - specific type which will be weighted
        Returns:
        date of the weighted middle, not necessarily present in data. Returns null if input data is empty, or doesn't have entries with the given type
